{"tid":2213530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不一樣的中秋","createTime":"2020-09-22T14:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T15:23:04.000Z","uid":275478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f53de3a27182790d0387c856436bbd770aef24","tid":2213530,"uid":275478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"12名港人被內地刑事拘留將近一個月，其中李子賢的父母接受本台專訪。他的媽媽形容，兒子熱愛香港，自從他失蹤後，寢食難安，盼望下星期中秋節能一家團聚。<br />\n<br />\n李子賢爸爸表示，不覺得內地有陽光司法，拒絕官派律師。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3862318057209555/?vh=e&amp;extid=HOH2g13lt5Nqlu89&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3862318057209555%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DHOH2g13lt5Nqlu89%26d%3Dn&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I25bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=c1c00e2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3862318057209555/?vh=e&amp;extid=HOH2g13lt5Nqlu89&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc33f40ccabb217e9a2025c500d954786654a32","tid":2213530,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，<del>好大機會</del><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong>包括</strong></ins></span><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I25bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=ec3a85bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"}]}